 AI Feedback Sentiment Automation

Overview: This project is an AI-powered automation workflow built using Make.com. It collects client feedback, analyzes the sentiment using AI, and automatically sends structured insights to Slack.
The goal is to help teams quickly understand customer opinions without manually reviewing responses.


Features:
* Collects client/customer feedback automatically
* Uses AI to classify sentiment (Positive & Negative)
* Structures results for easy interpretation
* Sends real-time updates to Slack channels
* Fully automated workflow (no manual intervention)

How It Works
1. Feedback is submitted via a form 
2. Make.com triggers the automation workflow
3. AI processes the text and determines sentiment
4. The result is formatted into a readable summary
5. A notification is sent directly to Slack


Tech Stack
* Make.com (automation)
* Make.com API (sentiment analysis)
* Slack API (notifications)


Use Cases
* Customer feedback analysis
* Product reviews monitoring
* Support ticket sentiment tracking
* Community feedback insights


